high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn right to face the tomato on the corner of the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Take a step to the left to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the tomato slice on the edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice and place it on the edge of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and face the sink in front of you.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Face the counter to your right.
Slice the tomato in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave on your left.
Place the knife in the microwave in front of you and close it.
Turn left and face the counter to your right.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave to your left.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave in front of you and take it out.
Face the sink on your left.
Place the tomato slice by the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice near the sink.

high_descs: turn around, walk to fridge, turn left, walk to the sink
pick up the knife that is on the floor
turn right to face the counter
cut the tomato that is on the counter
take a step to the right to face microwave
put the knife in the microwave, close it
take a step to the left
pick up a tomato slice that is on the counter
take a step to the right to face the microwave
put the tomato slice in the microwave, close it, turn it on, take tomato out
take a left to face the sink
put the tomato slice on the counter in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: put a cooked tomato slice on the counter
